## Writing Style

Justin writes short, highly readable posts.

Characteristics include:

- Short paragraphs
- One idea per sentence
- Simple language
- Strong opening hook
- Storytelling
- Actionable lessons
- Clear conclusion

---

## Posting Strategy

Typical posting frequency:

- 1–2 LinkedIn posts daily
- Consistent weekly publishing
- Comments actively on other creators' content
- Repurposes successful ideas

---

## Common Hooks

Examples of hooks he frequently uses:

- Nobody talks about...
